name: Alchemaniac
effects: Players will receive 15/30/50% extra coins when casting High Level Alchemy on items.

name: Arcane Conduit
effects: Runes and magic weapon charges have a 40/60/90% chance to be saved.

name: Armadylean Decree
effects: When wielding four Armadylean items, enchanted bolt effects have a 25/50/100% increased chance to activate.

name: Bandosian Might
effects: When wielding four Bandosian items, the player's max melee hit is increased by 1/2/4 for every attack speed a weapon has.

name: Barbarian Pest Wars
effects: Reward currency earned for playing the following minigames are increased by x2/x3/x4: Honour points from Barbarian Assault Commendation points from Pest Control Zeal Tokens from Soul Wars

name: Bottomless Quiver
effects: Ranged ammunition and ranged weapon charges have a 40/60/90% chance to be saved, excluding chinchompas. The chances to save ammunition and charges are rolled separately.

name: Catch Of The Day
effects: All types of Fishing activities have a 1 in 300/200/80 chance, per catch, to roll the rare drop table once.

name: Certified Farmer
effects: Farming yields have a 25/50/100% chance to be doubled, and are converted to bank notes upon harvest.

name: Chef's Catch
effects: Players have a 20/35/50% chance of cooking a raw fish upon catching them. Cooking experience is granted, even if players do not have the level required to cook them normally.

name: Chinchonkers
effects: Catching chinchompas grant 50/100/100% more Hunter experience. At level 3, players will receive two chinchompas per successful capture.

name: Clued In
effects: The drop rate of scroll boxes from NPCs are increased to 1 in 30/25/15.

name: Deeper Pockets
effects: Players have a 20/50/100% chance to receive double loot when pickpocketing NPCs. This stacks multiplicatively with rogue equipment.

name: Dine & Dash
effects: Players have a 10/20/50% chance to receive an extra piece of cooked food while cooking. Though no extra Cooking experience is gained when this occurs, the extra food is automatically sent to the player's bank.

name: Divine Restoration
effects: Players will have their prayer points restored by one every 15/9/3.6 seconds.

name: Dragon On A Bit
effects: Players have a 10/20/40% chance to save the materials used whilst crafting dragonhide armour. The saved materials are automatically sent to the player's bank.

name: Enchanted Jeweler
effects: Each enchantment spell cast will enchant up to 5/10/25 pieces of jewellery, granting the full Magic experience.

name: Golden Brick Road
effects: When a mark of grace appears when training on a Rooftop Agility Course, 4,000/7,000/15,000 coins will appear alongside it.

name: Grave Robber
effects: The amount of hallowed marks received when looting coffins within the Hallowed Sepulchre is increased by 50/150/300%.

name: Homewrecker
effects: Players have a x2/x3/x4 chance of receiving bird nests when chopping trees, and are sent to the bank rather than falling to the ground.

name: Hot On The Trail
effects: Players have a 2/5/10% chance to obtain a scroll box whilst lighting logs via Firemaking.

name: Imcando's Apprentice
effects: Players have a 20/50/75% chance to craft an extra piece of gemmed jewellery, granting Crafting experience for the extra jewellery. Note that players must have spare inventory space to obtain the extra jewellery.

name: Just Druid!
effects: Players will receive 10/20/40% extra Herblore experience for each grimy herb cleaned.

name: Larger Recharger
effects: Players will have their special attack energy restored by 10% every 25/20/10 seconds.

name: Livin' On A Prayer
effects: The drain rate of activated prayers are reduced by 15/30/60%.

name: Message In A Bottle
effects: The chance of receiving clue geodes, nests, and bottles from skilling are increased by x3/x5/x10.

name: Mixologist
effects: Players will have a 25/50/100% chance to mix a 4-dose potion rather than a 3-dose potion, with a 20/50/100% chance to save the secondary ingredient.

name: Molten Miner
effects: If applicable, ores mined have a 20/50/100% chance to be smelted into bars. Smithing experience is granted, even if players do not have the level required to smelt them normally.

name: Mother's Magic Fossils
effects: The chance of receiving golden nuggets from the Motherlode Mine is increased by x2/x3/x4. The amount of pizazz points received from activities in the Mage Training Arena is increased by x2/x3/x4. The chance of receiving fossils from activities on Fossil Island is increased by x2/x3/x4.

name: Plank Stretcher
effects: Players will have a 10/20/50% chance to save their planks whilst training Construction.

name: Praying Respects
effects: Remains are automatically buried/scattered, granting 50/100/200% of the usual Prayer experience. League experience multipliers are applied.

name: Pro Tips
effects: Players will receive 30/50/100% more bolt tips per gem whilst making them.

name: Profletchional
effects: Fletching logs and stringing bows grant 30/50/100% more Fletching experience.

name: Rock Solid
effects: Iron, sandstone, and granite rocks have a 25/50/75% chance to not be depleted upon being mined.

name: Rogues' Chompy Farm
effects: The chance of successfully cracking the wall safe at the end of the Rogues' Den maze is increased by 10/20/40%. Each chompy bird killed will count as 2/3/4 kills when checking chompy kill-count via the ogre bow. The amount of points earned from the Tithe Farm is increased by x2/x3/x4.

name: Rooty Tooty 2x Runeys
effects: Players have a 20/40/80% chance to receive an extra rune for each rune crafted.

name: Rumple-Bow-String
effects: The Spin Flax spell gives 10/15/27 bow strings instead of the usual 5.

name: Rune Escape
effects: Players will no longer receive mind (lv-1)/body (lv-2)/elemental runes (lv-3) when crafting runes at the Ourania Altar.

name: Saradominist Defence
effects: When wielding four Saradominist items, the player's max hit is increased by 2/5/10 if they have taken damage in the last 3.6 seconds.

name: Seedy Business
effects: Players have a 10/25/50% chance to save their seed upon planting it in a farming patch.

name: Slash & Burn
effects: Players have a 20/35/50% chance of burning logs upon chopping them. Firemaking experience is granted, even if players do not have the level required to burn them normally.

name: Slay 'n' Pay
effects: Players will earn 10/20/50% more slayer reward points upon completing a slayer task.

name: Slay All Day
effects: Players will heal 1/2/3 hitpoints for every monster killed as part of a slayer task.

name: Smithing Double
effects: Players have a 5/15/30% chance to smith an extra item when smithing items at an anvil, granting Smithing experience for the extra item. Extra items will drop to the floor if players have no inventory space.

name: Smooth Criminal
effects: The chance to successfully pickpocket NPCs is increased by 15/25/50%. At level 2, players will no longer take damage when stunned by a failed pickpocket attempt. The gloves of silence and Ardougne Diary bonus will stack.

name: Special Discount
effects: Special attacks whose energy cost is greater than 50/40/25% will cost 50/40/25% energy instead.

name: Superior Tracking
effects: Superior slayer monsters have a 1 in 150/100/30 chance of spawning during a slayer task for eligible slayer monsters.

name: Tactical Duelist
effects: Melee weapon charges have a 20/40/80% chance to be saved.

name: Thrall Damage
effects: The max hit of thralls are increased by x2/x3/x4. Damage is rounded up.

name: Unholy Ranger
effects: The player's accuracy for ranged weapons is increased by 30/60/100% when they have no prayer points remaining. Excludes the dwarf multicannon.

name: Unholy Warrior
effects: The player's accuracy for melee weapons is increased by 12/20/30% when they have no prayer points remaining.

name: Unholy Wizard
effects: The player's accuracy for magic attacks is increased by 40/70/125% when they have no prayer points remaining.

name: Venomaster
effects: The player's attacks have a chance to inflict poison that starts at 3/5/7 damage. Players will gain poison immunity at level 2, and venom immunity at level 3.

name: Zamorakian Sight
effects: When wielding four Zamorakian items, the player's accuracy for magic attacks is increased by 50/125/250%.
